{"tid":576476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不顧中方反對　美參院通過《台灣旅行法》川普簽署後將立即生效","createTime":"2018-03-01T02:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T06:11:47.000Z","uid":35790,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4635cf6f69204ee8cc653e79988f88ba486255d1","tid":576476,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"不顧中方反對　美參院通過《台灣旅行法》<br />\n<br />\n2018/03/01 10:05<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院不顧中方反對，昨日在全體院會通過《台灣旅行法》，鼓勵台美官員互訪。該法案在美國總統川普簽署後將立即生效。<br />\n<br />\n路透報導，《台灣旅行法》今年1月先在眾院無異議通過，送交參議院後，昨日也一致表決通過《台灣旅行法》。<span style=\"color: red;\">根據該法，美國必須允許所有階層官員赴台訪問，也應給予台灣官員入境美國的許可，並在「在互相尊敬的條件下」安排台美官員互訪，同時鼓勵台灣經濟與文化代表在美國發展業務。</span><br />\n<br />\n在兩院通過此案後，法案會送交川普簽署。白宮目前未回應，川普何時簽屬此案。若川普拒簽國會兩院一致通過的法案，將為十分罕見的案例。<br />\n<br />\n中國官方媒體新華社上月初曾報導指出，中方對此法案嚴重不滿，稱法案違背一中原則。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180301/1305980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180301%2F1305980%2F&d=gv%2B9msUjp3Mb%2FfzWMe%2F9flKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=c3b5b5e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180301%2F1305980%2F&h=58a3d0c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180301/1305980/</a>"},{"pid":"e1022694787e27b5a0bfe5df1e61539b3620b5e0","tid":576476,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335955fb83ba8d2788671bc36a86ec71f9352155","tid":576476,"uid":135313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af8410b9c79a3e9bc4249cb4fe7a6f2ba892f16","tid":576476,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy